    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 977.6, y: 53.6}
    <Text>k__BackingField: State-engineered masculinity refers to masculinity that
      aligns with China's nationalistic values and interests. It seeks to emphasise
      China's economic and cultural prowess by having men possess both the traits
      of the traditional Confucian junzi and demonstrating patriotism.
