    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 179.2, y: 64}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Contemporary China masculinity is, in some sense, a hybrid
      masculinity that blends state-engineered masculinity and softness.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
